room_title: Escape room "The Da Vinci Code" by Escape Room Kansas City in Kansas City
room_address: 30 W Pershing Rd, Kansas City, MO 64108
room_description: An unforgettable adventure where you will travel to the times of the great Leonardo Da Vinci. Plunge into a setting that has been thought through and decorated to the very tiny detail. Secret compartments, mechanical puzzles, unexpected twists and turns. Not only do you have to get out of the room, but also find the Holy Grail.
